extends Enum<CompletionState>
    Enumerates the possible completion states of a Future, providing a unified way to determine whether a task is still running, completed successfully, cancelled, or failed due to an exception.

    This utility supports various implementations of Future, including CompletableFuture and ForkJoinTask, and offers a consistent method to assess their completion status.

    Use the of(Future) method to determine the CompletionState of a given Future.
